User Stories:

Users should see a menu before starting the game (Est. 1 hour)
The game will have textured graphics, and a nice gui (Est. 2 hours) (Completed)
The game will display a victory image, with the option to restart (Est. 30 minutes) (Completed)
Users will be able to see how fast they completed the game (Est. 30 minutes)
Users should see moving Monsters, Gold, and a Player animate between various positions (Est. 2 hours) (Removed - Completed)
Other functionality features to improve game quality (Est. 3 hours) (Completed)


